text: Liana Ghazaryan (; born 15 February 2000) is an Armenian footballer who plays as a defender for Gyumri and the Armenia women's national team. ==International career== Ghazaryan capped for Armenia at senior level in a 1–1 friendly draw against Lithuania on 6 March 2020. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Armenian women's footballers Category:Armenia women's international footballers
